verbose_text: As same as wild-type TBC1D8, TBC1D8 RYQ / AAA mutant inhibited PK activity, suggesting that the elimination of Rab-GAP activity of TBC1D8 did not influence the inhibitory effects of TBC1D8 on PK activity.
